cu.explanation_en: Setting the MNC to 999 exceeds the valid range for Mobile Network Code (typically 2-3 digits, 000-999 but reserved values), causing invalid PLMN configuration and network registration failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FrequencyStart to 100 exceeds the valid range (0-63), causing invalid PRACH configuration and RACH setup failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FrequencyStart 設定為 100 超過有效範圍（0-63），會導致無效的 PRACH 配置和 RACH 設定失敗。
